This spectacular 1.6 acre property rests high above the glistening waters of the Long Island Sound and Larchmont Harbor, with over 500 ft of private shoreline, a deep water dock, a jetty, and an area for swimming or launching a small watercraft. Magnificently sited on a lush promontory adjacent to Manor Park, this beautiful 8,182 SF, 1898 Victorian is designed to highlight the gorgeous panoramas from every room. Experience unobstructed views from the wraparound porch, bluestone patio, in-ground pool & spa. An original stable is now a 3 bed, 2 bath guest house with chic-retro kitchen. At the heart of this 3-level turreted icon is a great room that soars 2 stories with stairway to a glass cupola. Each space melds period grandeur with glamour. This home is unrivaled.
25 Park Avenue, Larchmont, NY $11,300,000
7 Bedrooms
6/2 Baths
Don’t miss out on the opportunity to own this extraordinary waterfront home, listed with @Mimi.Magarelli. Learn more via the link below.
https://wpsir.co/25ParkAvenue

La Koubba has six bedrooms in the main house with two on the ground floor and four on the second floor. Five of the bedrooms have king size beds, one bedroom has two twin beds, and all the bedrooms have en-suite bathrooms. Air-
conditioning is available throughout. The seventh bedroom comes courtesy of a guest cottage with a private entrance from the courtyard. Contact @caribb.ian for more information!

A walk up the winding staircase to the grandiose entryway of Villa Oasis, is a walk into treasure found on Grace Bay beach. A property steeped in history you feel like a true Islander from the moment you step foot into the Grand Room and stare up at the incredible vaulted ceiling and out to the expansive pool deck and the mesmerizing blues of Grace Bay. There is a homeliness and warmth to this property that is unmatched in my experience, a throwback to a bygone era; the charm and class are evident in every detail throughout both levels of the Villa and the guest house. You can see the love and passion wherever you turn. Perfect for families, friends and entertaining the open floor plan allows for the Chef’s kitchen to be connected to the spacious dining and living areas. Through the sliding doors and down the shortest path to the powder white sand of Grace Bay beach, you are literally on the water, and I cannot think of any other property that has such proximity to the shoreline.

Windhaven Kitesurfing Village is a boutique, resort real estate offering situated on 2.23 acres of prime Long Bay beachfront land with an incredible 158 feet of pristine, white sandy beach frontage. Consisting of three free-standing villas completed in 2012, Windhaven boasts more than 6,000 square feet of living space. The property has been beautifully designed and landscaped with meticulous attention to detail and an emphasis on vacationers enjoying a 5-star experience. The location on the South Shore of Providenciales is optimal, allowing visitors to choose total relaxation on a private beach setting or partake in an abundance of activities including kiteboarding, snorkeling, diving, horseback riding, and fishing. Gourmet restaurants, bars, and shopping are just a short drive away in Grace Bay. Among the three villas at Windhaven are Villa Beaufort, a 4-bedroom, 2-story luxury villa that comfortably sleeps 8 adults, the 2-bedroom Villa Caracol, and 2-bedroom Villa Olitas. Each beachfront villa features luxury ensuite bathrooms with outdoor showers for each bedroom, full kitchens, comfortable living rooms, and private patios perfect for lounging or dining alfresco.
